# Anything that bloats the build context or duplicates what `composer install`
# / `npm ci` will produce inside the container.
.git
.github
node_modules
vendor
storage/logs/*
storage/framework/cache/*
storage/framework/sessions/*
storage/framework/views/*
storage/app/*
storage/uploads
storage/backups
public/build

# ─── Large local data / scratch — must NEVER enter the image ─────────────────
# Local test corpora and working dirs: 16GB+ of sample digital objects under
# ./uploads, a FamilySearch import set, a Python venv, scratch dirs. With these
# in the build context the image ballooned to ~26GB; excluded it is a few
# hundred MB. None are read at build or runtime (uploads live on a volume/NAS).
/uploads
/FamilySearch
/venv
/stuff
/site
/audit_outputs
/docs
*.log
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!docker/.env.docker.example
docker/.env.docker
.idea
.vscode
*.sql.gz
docs/papers
docs/images
docs/assets

# ─── HARD RULE: Heratio is an AI client, never a host ────────────────────────
# Per feedback_ai_remote_only.md and project policy: AI features run on a
# separate GPU host via HTTP. The Heratio container must NEVER bundle model
# weights, AI runtimes, or large binary blobs - the published image at
# ghcr.io/archiveheritagegroup/heratio is fully public, and shipping models
# in it would (a) violate model licenses, (b) bloat the image by GBs, and
# (c) imply a local LLM exists when there isn't one.
#
# These globs reject anything that looks like a model file or AI runtime
# from sneaking into the build context, even if a developer accidentally
# has them in their working tree.
*.safetensors
*.gguf
*.ggml
*.bin
*.pt
*.pth
*.onnx
*.h5
*.ckpt
*.tflite
*.msgpack
# NOTE: do NOT add '**/models/' or '**/checkpoints/' here. They match real
# source - packages/ahg-ai-compliance/resources/views/models/*.blade.php and
# packages/*/src/Models/ - and silently drop it from the image (that admin page
# then 500s). Model WEIGHTS are already caught by the extension globs above and
# by the Dockerfile's build-time AI-leak guard.
**/.cache/huggingface/
**/.cache/torch/
**/.cache/whisper/
**/.cache/ollama/
**/ollama/
**/llama.cpp/
**/whisper.cpp/
**/transformers_cache/
